urg following the closing of the fund adoption expected on or around june   the ucits funds will be distributed internationally by ivy funds distributor inc and will be managed by ivy its affiliate waddell  reed investment management company previously served as subadvisor to the funds both ivy entities are subsidiaries of waddell  reed financial inc ivy funds intends to create a new subsidiary of ivy funds distributor inc to be called ivy global investors inc that will be responsible for the distribution of the ucits fund range it also is intended that the sicav be renamed ivy global investors with that name attaching to each of the subfunds within the sicav eg ivy global investors asset strategy fund “this transaction enables us both to serve the nonresident customer market through national brokerdealer firms in the united states and to establish greater international distribution of ivy’s investment management capabilities” said thomas w butch president and ceo of ivy funds distributor inc “it expands our distribution network as well as the range of investors that can access the investment management expertise offered through the ivy funds” subfunds of the sicav included in the fund adoption transaction are emg ivy asset strategy fund and emg ivy high income fund which have combined assets under management of approximately  million three other subfunds of the sicav  are under review in luxembourg emg ivy us mid cap growth fund emg ivy us large cap growth fund and emg ivy science and technology fund as part of the transaction ivy funds expects to hire approximately eight former emg employees principally involved in sales and marketing going forward emg will partner with ivy through the distribution of the ivy products in numerous offshore jurisdictions in italy brazil and certain middle eastern markets as well as through an emg sicav currently in the process of formation in the management of a fundoffunds ucits that invests in various offshore active funds including ivymanaged subfunds “smart beta” funds and etfs we are very pleased to be able to continue to work closely with emg as they help distribute ivy products in a number of important global markets and include ivy in their planned fundoffunds products said butch we have worked together effectively and expect this will continue and even be enhanced as we go forward through its subsidiaries waddell  reed financial inc nyse wdr provides investment management and financial planning services to clients throughout the us the firm had approximately  billion in total assets under management at march   ivy investment management company serves as investment advisor to the ivy funds while ivy funds distributor inc serves as principal underwriter and distributor to the ivy funds this release does not constitute or contain an offer solicitation recommendation or investment advice with respect to the purchase of the ucits fund described herein or any security prospective investors should carefully consider fund objectives risks charges tax considerations and expenses and other relevant information before investing for this and more information on the selector management fund sicav please request a prospectus and read it carefully before you invest prospective investors should also consult their professional advisers as to the suitability of any investment in light of their particular circumstances and applicable citizenship residence or domicile selector management fund sicav has been authorized in luxembourg as an undertaking for collective investments in transferable securities ucits shares of selector management fund sicav are only available for certain nonus persons in select transactions outside the united states the views expressed herein represent the opinions of ivy investment management co and are not intended as a forecast or guarantee of future results for any product or service investment return and principal value will fluctuate and it is possible to lose money by inve