first mutual funds in the united states its first offices were in department stores continental investment corporation of boston bought waddell  reed for  million in  liberty national insurance holding company later renamed torchmark corporation acquired it for  million in  torchmark spun it off in  in a deal where for  torchmark shares held torchmark shareholders received  shares of waddell  reed referencesedit  market watch inc waddell  reed corporate overview  waddell  reed inc  company history fundinguniversecom retrieved    torchmark announces spinoff of waddell  reed  re birmingham ala oct  prnewswire alabama prnewswirecom retrieved   external linksedit home page retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlewaddellreedoldid categories companies listed on the new york stock exchangemutual fund familiescompanies based in overland park kansas navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version languages españolsvenska edit links this page was last edited on  july  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may apply by using this site you agree to the terms of use and privacy policy wikipedia® is a registered trademark of the wikimedia foundation inc a nonprofit organization privacy policy about wikipedia disclaimers contact wikipedia developers cookie statement mobile view ivy investment management company private company information  bloomberg july    pm et capital markets company overview of ivy investment management company snapshot people company over